ocessor architecture powering most personal computers and servers worldwide.", "Google is an American technology company specializing in internet search, online advertising, and cloud computing, headquartered in Mountain View, California. It created the Android mobile OS, Chrome browser, and Tensor custom chips."], "scores": [0.6595343355331985, 0.498652385306778, 0.37587054698397326, 0.3678759522139407, 0.3389595458632185], "model_name": "mpnet", "document_ids": ["Nvidia", "AMD", "OpenAI", "Intel", "Google"]}}